title: Introduction to C Programming
description: A comprehensive guide to C programming. Learn the basics of C, including variables, data types, and control structures. This course is suitable for beginners and provides a solid foundation for learning.

title: Introduction to Algorithms
description: Explore the world of algorithms with this introductory course. Topics include sorting, searching, and algorithm analysis. Suitable for beginners and those wanting to deepen their algorithmic knowledge.

title: Introduction to C++ for DSA
description: Learn C++ programming with a focus on Data Structures and Algorithms (DSA). Cover key concepts in C++, such as classes and objects. Suitable for programming enthusiasts.

title: Basic Data Structures
description: Discover essential data structures used in computer science. Topics include arrays, linked lists, stacks, and queues. Suitable for beginners and aspiring to be a programmers.

title: Introduction to OOP Python
description: Master Object-Oriented Programming (OOP) in Python. Learn about classes, inheritance, and polymorphism. Suitable for Python developers looking to advance their skills.

title: Software Engineering
description: Comprehensive coverage of the software development lifecycle. Topics include requirements, design, coding, testing, and project management. Suitable for software engineering enthusiasts.

title: Complete Web Development
description: Become a full-stack web developer with hands-on projects. Learn HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and backend development. Suitable for beginners and aspiring web developers.

title: Database (MySQL)
description: In-depth course on database design, SQL, and MySQL administration. Learn to create and manage databases, optimize queries, and ensure data integrity. Suitable for database enthusiasts.

title: Programming Problem Solving
description: Enhance your coding skills with practical problem-solving exercises. Solve coding challenges and improve your problem-solving abilities. Suitable for aspiring programmers.
